main_body:
Decision 1999/730/CFSP shall be amended as follows:
(a) in Article 3(1), the financial reference amount shall be replaced by EUR 1300000;
(b) in Article 4, second paragraph the date of "15 November 2000" shall be replaced by "15 November 2001";
(c) the Annex shall be replaced by the Annex to this Decision.
